Ya.

00:40:35.938 --> 00:40:37.273
Lucu sekali!

00:40:38.507 --> 00:40:39.508
Berikutnya.

00:40:40.075 --> 00:40:41.577
-Hah?
-Apa?

00:40:42.311 --> 00:40:43.479
Manusia?

00:40:43.546 --> 00:40:45.814
Sepertinya begitu, ya.

00:40:46.448 --> 00:40:48.183
Manusia memang.

00:40:48.250 --> 00:40:49.218
Manusia lain.

00:40:49.285 --> 00:40:51.420
-Apakah orang yang sama?
-Sepertinya begitu.

00:40:51.921 --> 00:40:53.122
Tapi mereka bukan hewan, kan?

00:40:53.622 --> 00:40:55.357
Yah, manusia kan makhluk hidup.

00:40:56.258 --> 00:40:57.660
Baiklah kalau begitu.

00:40:57.726 --> 00:40:59.161
Ya.

00:41:00.896 --> 00:41:03.499
Wah, manusia lagi!

00:41:03.566 --> 00:41:05.834
